{"tid":1255463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"621發夢遇到一位睿智老人","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:40:00.000Z","uid":219269,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b62ca5473ac024304cb3df71f669b00a784efac0","tid":1255463,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:37:47.000Z","msg":"隱約記得佢七十幾歲，姓許<br />\n滿頭白髮話自己由六月九開始一直發夢<br />\n發一個見證希望嘅夢，有好多人一齊出來同魔鬼<br />\n見到佢地咁勇敢又咁成熟覺得好欣慰<br />\n佢好有時事觸覺，知道咩係獨派，勇武同埋和理<br />\n佢認為今次係有好大機會美夢成真<br />\n印象好深刻嘅係佢唔係齋吹<br />\n佢話我地而家一啲都唔孤單，響呢條對抗魔鬼嘅路上<br />\n有一位金色頭髮嘅肥佬叔叔會聯同其他朋友一齊打擊佢<br />\n<br />\n我話我都知呢個金髮肥佬，但佢係生意人黎架，會同魔鬼達成協儀<br />\n佢笑一笑，話唔係做生意咁簡單，金髮肥佬同佢簽唔簽到都好<br />\n都會<span style=\"color: gold;\">用各種手段，持續打擊佢，直至將佢響世界第二嘅位置上踢佢落黎<br />\n之後個峰會唔係咩不得了嘅死線</span><br />\n<br />\n佢最後話好感激啲後生仔女為呢場夢付出咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但願各位醒來可以處處聞啼鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場夢仲未完，唔需要灰心喪志，我們並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5f3c3eba61470f7868169914618648c5cffcca","tid":1255463,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警民大和解】警方高層不代表前線 市民應支持前線警員!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251511\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e78842087403e0bb5c18f8ebfa5cee561f4323","tid":1255463,"uid":219269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb5f3c3eba61470f7868169914618648c5cffcca","tid":1255463,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rU8fFf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrU8fFf9.jpg&h=c6019c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【警民大和解】警方高層不代表前線 市民應支持前線警員!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251511\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"shared<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}